  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Norcross\" title=\"House Norcross\"><img alt=\"House Norcross.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/50px-House_Norcross.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/75px-House_Norcross.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/100px-House_Norcross.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Alester Norcross</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Norcross\" title=\"House Norcross\"><img alt=\"House Norcross.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/50px-House_Norcross.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/75px-House_Norcross.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/100px-House_Norcross.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Norcross\" title=\"House Norcross\">House Norcross</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_291_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">291&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Hosman_Norcross\" title=\"Hosman Norcross\">Hosman Norcross</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Delena_Florent\" title=\"Delena Florent\">Delena Florent</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alester Norcross</b> is the eldest son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hosman_Norcross\" title=\"Hosman Norcross\">Hosman Norcross</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Delena_Florent\" title=\"Delena Florent\">Delena Florent</a>. He has a younger brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Norcross\" title=\"Renly Norcross\">Renly</a>, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> half-brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Storm\" title=\"Edric Storm\">Edric Storm</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He is probably <a href=\"/index.php/Named_after\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named after\">named after</a> his mother's uncle, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Florent\" title=\"Alester Florent\">Alester Florent</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alester_Norcross&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</sp